        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[欢迎来到博客]]></title>
            <link>https://arcadia.cool/blog/welcome</link>
            <guid>https://arcadia.cool/blog/welcome</guid>
            <pubDate>Mon, 01 May 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[如果你想在本站发布你的文章，请阅读下方的内容。]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>如果你想在本站发布你的文章，请阅读下方的内容。</p><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Mb0m" id="发布流程">发布流程<a href="#发布流程" class="hash-link" aria-label="发布流程的直接链接" title="发布流程的直接链接">​</a></h2><h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Mb0m" id="1-部署本地环境">1. 部署本地环境<a href="#1-部署本地环境" class="hash-link" aria-label="1. 部署本地环境的直接链接" title="1. 部署本地环境的直接链接">​</a></h3><p>首先，你需要克隆本仓库到本地并进入根目录，然后进行下面的操作</p><p>安装依赖并运行本地开发服务器（预览）</p><div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_hVs1 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_NsmR"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_NGiJ thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_VNjo"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token function" style="color:#8250DF">npm</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token function" style="color:#8250DF">install</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:#8250DF">npm</span><span class="token plain"> run start</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup_IakM"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_m8IT" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_hnHf"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_F17t"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><p>默认情况下，系统浏览器会自动打开一个窗口 <a href="http://localhost:3000" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">http://localhost:3000</a></p><h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Mb0m" id="2-创建博客">2. 创建博客<a href="#2-创建博客" class="hash-link" aria-label="2. 创建博客的直接链接" title="2. 创建博客的直接链接">​</a></h3><p>在 <code>blog</code> 目录下创建一个 <code>.md</code> 或 <code>.mdx</code> 文件，文件名需要使用英文，格式为 <code>yyyy-mm-dd-文章标题.md</code>，例如：<code>2023-05-01-welcome.md</code>，之后你就可以在本地开发服务器的博客页面看到这篇文章了。</p><p>如果你需要在内容中添加图片等媒体资源，那么你需要在 blog 目录下按照命名规则建立一个文件夹例如 <code>2023-05-01-welcome</code>，然后将文件命名为 <code>index.md</code> 或 <code>index.mdx</code>，这样你就可以在博客中使用相对路径引用这些资源了。</p><div class="language-javascript codeBlockContainer_hVs1 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_NsmR"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-javascript codeBlock_NGiJ thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_VNjo"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">blog</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  └── </span><span class="token number" style="color:#005CC5">2023</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#D73A49">-</span><span class="token number" style="color:#005CC5">05</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#D73A49">-</span><span class="token number" style="color:#005CC5">01</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#D73A49">-</span><span class="token plain">welcome</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">      ├── index</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">.</span><span class="token property-access">md</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">      └── image</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">.</span><span class="token property-access">png</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup_IakM"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_m8IT" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_hnHf"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_F17t"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Mb0m" id="3-编辑博客">3. 编辑博客<a href="#3-编辑博客" class="hash-link" aria-label="3. 编辑博客的直接链接" title="3. 编辑博客的直接链接">​</a></h3><ul><li><h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Mb0m" id="博客前提">博客前提<a href="#博客前提" class="hash-link" aria-label="博客前提的直接链接" title="博客前提的直接链接">​</a></h4><p>这是一个示例，有关更多配置字段详见 <a href="https://docusaurus.io/zh-CN/docs/api/plugins/@docusaurus/plugin-content-blog#markdown-front-matter" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Markdown front matter</a></p><div class="language-javascript codeBlockContainer_hVs1 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_NsmR"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-javascript codeBlock_NGiJ thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_VNjo"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token operator" style="color:#D73A49">--</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#D73A49">-</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#005CC5">slug</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#D73A49">:</span><span class="token plain"> welcome # </span><span class="token function" style="color:#8250DF">路径</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token plain">url</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#005CC5">title</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#D73A49">:</span><span class="token plain"> 欢迎来到博客 # 标题</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#005CC5">authors</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#D73A49">:</span><span class="token plain"> user # 作者，需要在 authors</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">.</span><span class="token property-access">yml</span><span class="token plain"> 进行配置</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#005CC5">tags</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#D73A49">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">[</span><span class="token string" style="color:#C6105F">'教程'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#C6105F">'新手'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">]</span><span class="token plain"> # 底部标签</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token operator" style="color:#D73A49">--</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#D73A49">-</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup_IakM"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_m8IT" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_hnHf"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_F17t"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div></li><li><h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Mb0m" id="博客内容">博客内容<a href="#博客内容" class="hash-link" aria-label="博客内容的直接链接" title="博客内容的直接链接">​</a></h4><p>如果你不熟悉 Markdown 语法那么请先学习 <a href="https://docs.github.com/zh/get-started/writing-on-github/getting-started-with-writing-and-formatting-on-github/basic-writing-and-formatting-syntax" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Markdown 基本撰写和格式语法</a>，这是一个简单的语法，你可以很快学会。</p><p>本站基于 <a href="https://docusaurus.io/zh-CN" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Docusaurus</a> 构建，你可以通过官网教程学习使用 <a href="https://docusaurus.io/zh-CN/docs/markdown-features" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Markdown 特性</a></p></li></ul><h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Mb0m" id="4-提交并等待审核">4. 提交并等待审核<a href="#4-提交并等待审核" class="hash-link" aria-label="4. 提交并等待审核的直接链接" title="4. 提交并等待审核的直接链接">​</a></h3><p>  向仓库发起 Pull Requests 合并请求</p><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Mb0m" id="关于发布规则">关于发布规则<a href="#关于发布规则" class="hash-link" aria-label="关于发布规则的直接链接" title="关于发布规则的直接链接">​</a></h2><ol><li>内容需要与本项目相关  </li><li>内容需要经过审核  </li><li>内容需要是原创</li></ol>]]></content:encoded>
